user.about:
Hello Everyone!
Welcome to my closet🤗

Here you’ll find items: new with tags, new w/o tags, rare and gently used items. 

My motto is “you don’t have to spend a million bucks to look like a million bucks!” 

I love thrifting and finding classy outfits to wear and sell. Don’t worry, all clothes are kept in a cat-free room and our home is smoke-free as well. 

🌺🌺Everything I sell is something I have worn or would wear, meaning it’s in great condition, is good quality. If we have similar tastes, please follow me and visit my closet regularly. 

I’m always adding new items! I offer bundle discounts, but if you see an individual item you really want it, send me with an offer.🌺🌺

❗️IMPORTANT: I refuse to sell “garage sale” clothing. I would never sell something I wouldn’t personally wear. 

•••Quality over quantity•••

📭SHIPPING
I strive for the quickest shipping times possible! Please, keep in mind that in order to ship in the smallest possible packaging, some items may be received wrinkly. Sorry in advance! 

🔄RETURNS:
The condition of each item is reflected in the photos and descriptions. The buyer is responsible for reading and viewing the product information in it's entirety. If for some reason you are dissatisfied with your purchase please send me a private message so we can work something out. I encourage you to re-list if that is a viable option for you, however I request that you please take your own photos when doing so.

Thanks for stopping by and have a blessed day!❤️
